This is my favorite Guns N'Roses album. I have to admit that I hate Axl Rose as much as I love his voice but still this was a very good band that lasted for a very short time. I believe they could have still be together with all the original members but they were lazy, alcoholics and drug addicts. That's why today they are just a legend. And the so called Guns N'Roses (Chinese Democracy) Album is not Guns N'Roses at all. To me Guns N'Roses is the original Band that is in this album, not just Axl Rose with some other musicians. Anyways that's just my opinion I don't expect you to think like I do. Regardless of anything they had their glory days and this album captures GNR at their best.

